00:53:57.381 --> 00:54:00.950
wrote. Feigning hypotheses for explaining
all things

00:54:00.950 --> 00:54:05.770
mechanically and referring all other causes
to metaphysics.

00:54:05.770 --> 00:54:08.809
But Newton viewed this purely mechanical approach
as

00:54:08.809 --> 00:54:12.829
flawed. Newton instead wanted to deduce causes
from

00:54:12.829 --> 00:54:16.570
effects till we come to the very first cause.
