Newton

00:54:33.860 --> 00:54:36.640
wanted not merely to unfold the mechanism
of the world

00:54:36.640 --> 00:54:42.140
but he also wanted to learn, "whence is it
that nature doth nothing in vain and whence

00:54:42.140 --> 00:54:47.789
arises all that order
order and beauty which we see in the world."

